---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Breathe Cleaner with Indoor Air Quality (IAQ) | Comffordable Air" description="Enhance your home health with IAQ solutions in St. Petersburg, Tampa, and Clearwater. Whole-home purifiers, UV lights, and dehumidification.">
    <main>
        <section class="hero" style="min-height: 60vh; align-items: center;">
            <img src="/images/pic_4.png" alt="Indoor air quality and filtration specialist" class="hero-bg-img" loading="eager" width="1920" height="1080" />
            <div class="hero-overlay" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.55), rgba(0,0,0,0.75));"></div>
            <div class="container hero-content text-center" style="margin: 0 auto;">
                <h1 style="font-size: 4.5rem; text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); margin-bottom: 1rem;">Indoor Air Quality Services <span class="text-purple">Tampa Bay, FL</span></h1>
                <p style="margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.5rem; text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.8); max-width: 800px;">
                    Pure, crisp, and allergen-free air for your entire home.
                    Servicing <a href="/service-areas/st-petersburg-fl" class="text-purple" style="font-weight: 500;">St. Petersburg</a>,
                    <a href="/service-areas/tampa-fl" class="text-purple" style="font-weight: 500;">Tampa</a>, and
                    <a href="/service-areas/clearwater-fl" class="text-purple" style="font-weight: 500;">Clearwater</a>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="process-section" style="padding-top: 4rem;">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="services-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
                    <!-- Card 1 -->
                    <div class="glass-panel service-card animate-on-scroll" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100%; text-align: center;">
                        <h3 style="font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Air Purification</h3>
                        <div style="flex: 1;">
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                                Standard filters only catch the visible stuff. Our medical-grade HEPA and Merv-13 systems are designed to trap microscopic particles like pet dander, pollen, and smoke that often trigger asthma and allergies. By filtering your air at the intake, we ensure that every breath you take inside your home is crisp, clean, and truly refreshing.
                            </p>
                            <ul style="list-style: none; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); text-align: left;">
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> HEPA Whole-Home Filtration</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> Merv-13 Filter Upgrades</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> Particle Removal Diagnosis</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> Odor Reduction Technology</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; text-align: center; margin-top: auto;">BREATHE BETTER</a>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Card 2 -->
                    <div class="glass-panel service-card animate-on-scroll"
                        style="transition-delay: 0.2s; border-color: var(--primary-purple); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(30, 136, 229, 0.4); position: relative; display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100%; text-align: center;">
                        <div style="position: absolute; top: -15px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: var(--primary-purple); padding: 0.3rem 1rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; color: #fff;">
                            Most Effective</div>
                        <h3 style="font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">UV Air Scrubbers</h3>
                        <div style="flex: 1;">
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                                Think of this as "sunlight" for your lungs. Our advanced UV-C coil cleaners are installed directly into your air handler, where they neutralize mold spores, bacteria, and airborne viruses before they can enter your ductwork. This 24/7 silent protection prevents the "dirty sock" smell and ensures your internal system components stay as clean as the day they were installed.
                            </p>
                            <ul style="list-style: none; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); text-align: left;">
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> Advanced UV-C Coil Cleaners</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> Microbial Growth Prevention</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> Silent, 24/7 Protection</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> Low-Maintenance Efficiency</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; text-align: center; color: white; margin-top: auto;">GET IAQ QUOTE</a>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Card 3 -->
                    <div class="glass-panel service-card animate-on-scroll" style="transition-delay: 0.4s; display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100%; text-align: center;">
                        <h3 style="font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Dehumidification</h3>
                        <div style="flex: 1;">
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 2rem; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                                In Florida, humidity is the enemy of both comfort and health. High indoor moisture levels can lead to structural damage and are the primary breeding ground for mold and dust mites. Our whole-home dehumidifiers work in tandem with your AC to maintain a precise, comfortable humidity level between 45% and 55%, keeping your home's air feeling light and your surfaces dry.
                            </p>
                            <ul style="list-style: none; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--text-secondary); text-align: left;">
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> Precision Humidity Control</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> Mold Risk Mitigation</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> Improved AC Efficiency</li>
                                <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><i class="fa-solid fa-check text-purple"></i> Home Structural Protection</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; text-align: center; margin-top: auto;">REDUCE MOISTURE</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-dark), var(--bg-darker)); border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border); padding: 5rem 0;">
            <div class="container animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="section-title">
                    <span>Why It Matters Here</span>
                    <h2>Why Florida Homes Need IAQ Solutions</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="glass-panel" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.9; color: var(--text-secondary);">
                    <p>Florida's subtropical climate creates indoor air quality challenges that most homeowners never think about until a problem becomes impossible to ignore. With humidity regularly exceeding 80 percent during summer months, the interior of a Florida home becomes an ideal breeding ground for mold spores, dust mites, and bacteria. These threats thrive in warm, moist environments and circulate silently through your ductwork every time your AC runs.</p>
                    <p>Unlike homes in drier climates, Florida properties fight year-round humidity rather than a seasonal spike. This constant moisture pressure means even a well-sealed home can accumulate dangerous levels of airborne contaminants over time. Standard 1-inch air filters ship designed to protect the equipment, not your lungs. They capture only a fraction of the microscopic particles that actually affect your health, including pet dander, pollen, VOCs from household products, and fine particulate matter tracked in from outside.</p>
                    <p>Our IAQ solutions are built for the Florida environment. Whole-home HEPA and Merv-13 filtration systems intercept particles before they enter your living space. UV-C air scrubbers installed inside your air handler neutralize mold, bacteria, and viruses 24 hours a day without chemicals or maintenance. Whole-home dehumidifiers work alongside your AC to keep indoor humidity between 45 and 55 percent, the range the EPA recommends, dramatically reducing mold risk. Pair IAQ with <a href="/maintenance" class="text-purple" style="font-weight:600;">proactive care</a> and your system stays clean from the inside out. For Tampa Bay families, clean indoor air is a health necessity, not a luxury.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="faq-section" style="padding-bottom: 6rem;">

            <div class="container">
                <div style="height: 1100px"><iframe src="https://www.localmarketingmanager.com/api/questions/comffordable-air-solutions-frequently-asked-questions?textColor=%23000000&backgroundColor=%23ffffff&showTitle=true&borderRadius=10px&visibility=showAllExpanded&isTransparentBackgroundApplied=false" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; border: none;" loading="lazy" id="ai-seo-iframe"></iframe></div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
